    "INFORMATIVE:   It is considered that the proposed siting of the pole should be resisted as it would add to the street clutter, by virtue of the additional height and cabinet equipment, adversely affect the character and appearance of the King's Cross/St.Pancras Conservation Area, the Listed King's Cross Station and locally listed buildings.  Consideration should be given to relocating the pole behind the existing wall or attaching the antenna to existing street furniture such as the existing ten metre high lamppost situated 8.5 metres north of the proposed pole location, or to existing buildings."
